    "v4 task model: test_objects declare mandatory test_types and transport_options.",
    "5.5D multi-tower topology: 2 towers connected by interposer links.",
    "FPP per-die: only Tower 0 dies (die0, die1) have FPP hardware. Tower 1 dies (die2, die3) use serial TAP only.",
    "Per-die BIST engines: each die with BIST has its own engine. 3 BIST engines across 3 dies.",
    "Cross-tower interconnects: more interconnect test (EXTEST) tasks than simple 3D stacks.",
    "Tower 1 access goes through die0 STAP to die2 STAP, adding more serial overhead.",
    "Thermal RC parameters differ by tower position."
